Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.81,0:00:04.54,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The rhythm of the wind clears reasoning,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:06.42,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Always confirming that vital clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:08.63,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Jewel robbers are on the loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.78,0:00:10.63,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This incident can't delay it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:12.93,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Recognizing that single truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.93,0:00:14.43,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:16.72,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.24,0:01:45.48,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}With the help of the murdered Itakura{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s diary,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:50.63,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I followed up on my lead to the Black Organization\Nwith the help of Professor Agasa, which led us...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:52.42,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}to Itakura{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s cottage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:55.07,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:03.39,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yo, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:06.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Vodka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:09.37,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You're there, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've been discovered!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.22,0:02:14.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They know we failed to open the e-mail in this cottage!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:15.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:17.26,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:21.35,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I know you're in that cottage!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:28.35,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You better pick up the phone, Itakura{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:30.10,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.55,Title,,0,0,0,,Contact With the Black Organization\N(Pursuit Chapter)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:44.81,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:48.43,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I know you're in that cottage!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:51.73,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You better pick up the phone, Itakura{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:03:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have no choice but to run out\Nthe back door, despite the snowstorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:05.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:08.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's pretty dark in here, so I had\Ntrouble finding the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:10.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}H-Hey, hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The snowstorm seems to have caused a blackout in this entire area.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's also why I couldn't open the e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what you get for trying to get an e-mail in a cottage like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:23.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:26.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's the answering machine working if there's a blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:35.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, blackouts are common around here when it snows, so I got a phone with a battery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:39.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. Makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:45.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how did you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.38,0:03:51.22,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We know everything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:50.35,Signs,,0,0,0,,Turn the lights on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:56.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you've been watching my cottage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We weren't, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:08.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Either way, that doesn't matter. I hope you finished that operating system.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:13.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is someone else there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:16.90,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, answer me. What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:18.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:20.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-The wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the wind blowing against the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:27.07,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ah, I heard it was snowing heavily there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:30.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I can't use the PC.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but could you tell me directly where and when I should deliver the OS?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:40.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:42.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm only going to say it once, so pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:46.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know Kenbashi Station, the one under construction?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:49.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That fancy one they want to add to the Tohto Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:54.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow at midnight, in that station's lowest level.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to {the front of }coin locker #0032.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:01.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to bring the OS.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:04.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:05.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.77,0:05:07.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:10.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to go into hospital from tomorrow evening for a scan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:15.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you know, I have heart issues...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't tell me that you haven't actually finished the OS.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:21.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This better not be a trick to buy time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:26.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've already finished it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:28.41,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then when would be good?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be released from the hospital in three or four days...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:34.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, about five days from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:37.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fool, we can't wait that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just cancel your appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:43.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I finally got an appointment with this renowned heart surgeon,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:45.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't cancel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want me to give it to you before\NI get hospitalized, it'll have to be today,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:51.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the construction workers will be at the station from dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:55.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's not good for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:56.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine. Four then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:06:00.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 4 AM, four hours from now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:02.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,bring the OS to the place I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:04.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F-Four hours?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:07.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the way from Gunma to Tōkyō?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:11.20,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's wrong? If you finished it,\Nit shouldn't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:16.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll have it in four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I want you to assure me of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Promise me this isn't a trick so you can ambush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could take it by force,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:32.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but then you would lose all means of accessing the disk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:37.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like they said, you're an old bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, four hours it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:43.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{In front of}At coin locker #0032 in Kenbashi Station's lowest level.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:45.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:46.15,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:52.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:54.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:59.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you want to do what they're asking and take the operating system to them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:01.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:06.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just manipulated the conversation to move the delivery to 4 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:09.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,by pretending to be desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:11.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the morning, they'll probably broadcast the news of Itakura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:21.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they learn he's dead, both the deal and the clues we got will become useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:23.83,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The jewel thieves are still...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, no radio station reported it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Then, your plan was to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:30.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:37.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I planned to reply to their e-mail to move\Nthe meeting time up anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:39.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.41,0:07:42.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get rid of any traces that we were here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:45.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and get out of this cottage in your Beetle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:47.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:51.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They could be watching the cottage from nearby, couldn't they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:57.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if they see us get into the car out front?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:02.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Vodka or his associates were nearby,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:08.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they'd have known I was lying about the blackout and being unable to use the PC.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:10.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:13.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you asked me to turn on the lights, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, we know they're not anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:20.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,where they can see this cottage's lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:26.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They only found this place because that mail has a program that traces where it failed to be opened from,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:32.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Giving them exactly where that computer system is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we can get some of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:40.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If this disk contains a special program that can be used to commit crimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:46.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially if they're dangerous\Ncrimes, we'll have them arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:50.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we tell the police, they can go stake out the station,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:54.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and they'll walk right into our trap and get arrested!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:55.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:01.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, it's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He password-protected the OS, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:10.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like with the mail, Itakura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and those guys established a password for using the OS.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:12.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then copy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:15.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't do that either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:17.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's copy-protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without proof, the police can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:24.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't those guys always carry guns?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we report to the police that there will be a deal involving guns, they'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't even know how many guys from the Organization are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:36.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, with only a small group on our side, there's a good chance they'd be seriously injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:39.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unless we find out what they're up to,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:42.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and show the police evidence of how dangerous and large this Organization is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as well as gather a large police force with appropriate equipment, it will be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:55.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's frustrating. We know where they are and still can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there's something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:01.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's rather dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:05.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, do you mean to meet them in person?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:10.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:12.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Ah, probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's a flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:23.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll have to call the nearest petrol station and ask them to bring a spare tire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:25.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:29.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody's gonna bring a tire here this late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, then we'll have to be patient and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we do that, we won't make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:42.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is a message from God to keep you out of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:45.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:49.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A-A car...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:54.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:10:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:03.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, we just got a flat tire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:07.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need to get back to Tōkyō. Could you give us a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:09.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To Tōkyō?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:11.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:14.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine, we're going that way anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.71,0:11:17.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gramps, do you know these roads?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:19.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:21.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you sit in the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid, you go in the back seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:25.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:35.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, lady, I saw you were sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:38.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all right, I was just taking a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:48.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.61,0:11:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a foreign car, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:53.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, is this car yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:54.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:58.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though I'm a bit tired of it, and was thinking of buying another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:03.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you must be rich, because this is a very expensive car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:05.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:09.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might not look like it, but he's the heir to a big company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:16.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:24.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was a close call.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Snowy roads sure are dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:30.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, just drive safely and carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:37.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, didn't you hear a strange sound just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:40.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? I didn't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:44.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stuff in the boot probably moved around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:46.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't even think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:52.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember?\NI hate cigarette smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:54.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Ah, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:55.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:59.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To go to Tōkyō, take a left here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:01.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:04.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it stopped snowing, we'll probably get there by 3 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:11.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what were you doing in Gunma?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:13.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you take your grandson skiing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:16.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:28.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, be more careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry, I knew we shouldn't have taken a snowy road.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:43.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:46.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}These guys are pretty strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:52.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't tell me they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:08.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you stop that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:12.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many times have we been honked at? {Are you trying to crash?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:15.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you? I'm not good on snowy roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:20.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's right, mister,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:24.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have to drive carefully since this\Ncar is exhausted before its inspection.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:29.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This car is coming up for inspection soon, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:30.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:35.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:40.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sticker on the windshield has the number "2" on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:49.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that sticker tell you by its color and\Nnumber when the car is due for inspection?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:56.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's this year's color, so it's obvious it has to be inspected by the end of February.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:59.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:03.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got a reminder in the mail the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But boy, when did you see that? The sticker is covered with snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:12.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, I saw it when an oncoming car passed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:17.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the headlights shine on it, the number on the outside shows through the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:31.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it was a 2 from the back, but it's really a 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's strange, you already got a reminder in the mail for February.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:40.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:42.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:47.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I told you earlier, he's the heir to a large company.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he leaves all the details up to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:54.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He answered you casually, but the thing is, he doesn't have to worry about inspections.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:59.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should've taken that right turn, or we'll never make it to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:07.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, boy, stop bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:11.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, he's such a curious child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:14.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:15.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:24.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what've you been listening to, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:26.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:28.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was listening to the news on the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:30.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The news?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:33.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. There's all sorts of news today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About the economy improving,\Nabout Big Osaka's new manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:42.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And about the jewel thieves on the run.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:44.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so little, yet you really like the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:47.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:52.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have they caught the jewel thieves yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They said they were still\Nsomewhere near Gunma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they'll probably get caught soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Cause look...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police have checkpoints everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your licence, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:20.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:23.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:25.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Detective Yamamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:29.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Is that you, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:31.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Detective Yamamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:35.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This roadblock's meant to catch the jewel thieves, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:36.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:41.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were three thieves wearing balaclava{ski mask}s... {This might be a dialect phrase. A UK source uses balaclava}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:43.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After they hit a jewellery store in Gunma,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:49.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they abandoned the getaway car they stole in the mountains, and vanished somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.26,0:17:55.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But one of them's injured,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:57.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I don't think they could have gotten far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:17:58.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:06.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we were informed of the situation, we\Nhappened to be working on an investigation nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So when I got to the crime scene, I ran into the thieves, who were escaping from the jewellery store.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:15.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I drew out my pistol and told them
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:16.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Stop!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:18.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Stop or I'll shoot!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:19.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.65,0:18:21.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.94,0:18:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since the thieves didn't stop,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:26.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I fired off a warning shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:27.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:29.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:33.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I accidentally hit one of the thieves in the thigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:42.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway, the three of them probably either had another car ready in the mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:46.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or maybe they stole a vehicle that happened to be passing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:49.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't see anyone suspicious on the way, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:54.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're looking for someone going in a car that's not their own!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:58.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:05.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My car sprung a flat up in the mountains, so these people gave us a lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.59,0:19:07.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:10.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, your car...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.09,0:19:13.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll call the dealership in the morning to get it towed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.89,0:19:16.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I left my keys inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Won't something happen to your car?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:22.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:26.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The thieves might see it and drive off in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:28.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's definitely a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:34.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, shouldn't you be trying to catch\Nthat car rather than talking to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a yellow Beetle, you can't miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:39.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've heard your voices before...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:44.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're imagining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Can we go now, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm... I'm sorry, but could you please take that jacket off your lap?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:58.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you suspecting us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:02.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, look! I haven't been shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:03.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:05.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Agasa residence...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Gunma Police?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.36,0:20:27.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to Agasa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:31.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,his dealership was planning to pick up his car in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:34.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if we leave the car in the mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:37.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the thieves might try to use it to escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:41.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we decided to tow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So please tell him to come to the Gunma Police Station tomorrow for his car.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:51.07,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sorry for the bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:51.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:57.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What are they doing with his car up in Gunma at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:04.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Looks like Kudō{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10} stuck his nose in yet another case.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.96,0:21:07.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}For crying out loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:09.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Going off after some crime without sleeping...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:12.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's so fun about being a detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.99,0:21:24.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The spare tracking glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.78,0:21:38.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you heard me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:40.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be picking up the goods ahead of schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.41,0:21:43.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 4 AM, an hour from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:45.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lockers on the lowest level of Kenbashi Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.09,0:21:50.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell Gin that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.62,0:21:58.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make sure you have enough armed men around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.85,0:22:01.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might've gotten cold feet and called the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.99,0:22:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once the deal's done, we say goodbye to him for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:10.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were planning to get rid of him at Kenbashi Station to begin with.
